title: PVC wall panel extrusion line
title_uz: Devor uchun dekorativ PVC panellar ishlab chiqarish liniyasi
title_ru: Линия по производству декоративных панелей PVC для стен
short_description: The line of this model serves for the production of decorative panels used on the wall. The maximum width of the manufactured panel is 600 mm and the production capacity is 150-250 kg per hour.

short_description_ru: Линия этой модели предназначена для производства декоративных панно, используемых на стене. Максимальная ширина изготавливаемой панели 600 мм, производственная мощность 150-250 кг в час.

long_description:
The line of this model serves for the production of decorative panels used on the wall. The maximum width of the manufactured panel is 600 mm and the production capacity is 150-250 kg per hour.

 

 

Basic parameters
Extruder model US-SJZ65/132
Max. width of product 600 mm
Extruder motor 37 kW
Max. capacity 150-250 kg/hour
